728202f-a.folder: Willets Point Boulev & 15th Drive, Queens, NY
728202f-a.text:
Willets Point Boulevard, east side, between 15th Drive and 18th Avenue. This house was on the J. U. Roe property in 1873 and 1891 and on the Jonas Whitaker property in 1909.

P. L. Sperr                             July 28, 1935
